history.content:
If you're interested in cutting-edge data journalism, exploring new interactive data sets, or finding the clearest, most beautiful way to explain what's going on in Berkeley, apply to be a projects developer for the Daily Cal data projects team!

We make data stories, interactive graphics, news applications, charts, maps, and more. Here are some things we've done: projects.dailycal.org

Applications are due Friday, September 13 at 11:59 pm!

Apply here: apply.dailycal.org/editorial-department/projects-developer

Questions? Email projects@dailycal.org
